{"type": "article", "id": 24167, "title": "金发女郎和意大利面包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-21T07:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 135, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132623HCvumKrXeyo8bP9V.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一套结合了金发女郎的意大利面的包装，包装上只露出女郎的脸，用镂空的手法让不同形状的意大利面成为女郎的头发，形象而特别。她做了两种样式的盒子，直而长的面在长条形的盒子里，另两种弯曲的面在方形的盒子里，很巧妙，而白色的方盒子也是意大利面很少使用的一种，在货架上能够脱颖而出。设计者 Nikita 来自莫斯科，目前还没有上市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132621zMIPXnVZK897eOTx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.1890625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132621dZsok5epbcAxOrNg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1890625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132622rydYhnxtem4vgocb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1890625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132622S3uklAywoCTbsnOG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}